============================================\par
#  II. B  Other Items and Notes            #\par
============================================\par
\par
\par
Get these texts from the roulette, or some of them you can buy from Mel. To\par
play roulette, you need three coupons. To get a coupon, just do a mix that\par
always fails. Mel will give a coupon. When you have three, press the "talk"\par
button and then press the "roulette" button. If you don't see a good item, just\par
press the "B" button and go in the game again until you see a good item. When\par
you see an item you want, figure out what color the segment is that will give\par
you the good item. Now, to make the odds higher hold "A" while moving the\par
control stick. You can extend it to 12 sections for 60,000g which makes it ALOT\par
easier to win. When you get a text, press the "talk" button then press the\par
"present" button and finally select the text and press the "A" button and now\par
the mixes for that weapon will work.\par
\par
\par
\par
About these "beat difficulty 1" and such. To get these, you have to beat the\par
game very fast, shouldn't be tough, just don't waste time. I usually get them\par
so you shouldn't have a hard time getting them. Now difficulty 8 might be\par
another story... I can only beat the first level in this difficulty, and I can\par
only get to the final boss in difficulty 7 so I don't know what that gives you.\par
People that can beat these difficulties please email me and tell me what you\par
get so I can put them in this faq and you will be credited.\par
\par
\par
