=============================\par
#  IV. Essences/Materials   #\par
=============================\par
\par
These cards are used for mixing, and can be found in the game and bought.\par
Here are some ways to get them.\par
\par
1. Sometimes in adventure enemies will drop them.\par
\par
2. Cards sometimes are found in pots that have been broken.\par
\par
3. Some hidden areas hold lots of cards. In the sky arena, after you fall down\par
into a new area go up into the water. There you will find TONS of cards. Also,\par
in the elevator stage, break the glass in the beginning to find some cards.\par
\par
4. Also note that you cannot get stuff like fire dragon elemental cards and\par
angel rings in the levels, they must be bought or received from Pride.\par
